  geant-vmc-3.1.15a.ebuild, geant-vmc-4.2.14b.ebuild, geant-vmc-4.2.15.ebuild:
  Add subslot-dependency on sci-physics/root, rebuilding is needed on each ROOT
  version string change. For more details c.f. #505358 .

